            "question": "What is the delivery time for my order? ",
            "answer": "<p>For the Netherlands and Belgium, orders placed before 15:00 on working days will be delivered the next day. For European deliveries, this takes 3-10 working days, depending on the destination. You will always find the exact delivery time at checkout. This does not apply to custom socks; we print and design these individually, so they take up to 7 working days to process.<br/><br/></p>"
