          "settings": {
            "question": "What is the best way to wash my Sockeloen socks?",
            "answer": "<p>Wash at a maximum of 30 degrees.</p><p>Do not use fabric conditioner (this affects the elasticity and breathability).</p><p>Do not put them in the tumble dryer, but let them line dry.<br/></p>"
